We use Gmail calender to schedule tasks like cancellation requests / server move / restarts etc. Here the steps how to schedule a task in Gmail.
    
    Go to Gmail and click on calender. Choose Monthly View.
```diagram

```
    You can see the current scheduled tasks.

    Now click on the Date you want schedule a task.
 ```diagram

```
   
    
    Click on Create button.
```diagram

```


    Then schedule a task with following details

    Subject - Add a subject. Mention Ticket ID, Server name, Username, Reason
    Select All Day event
    Select Scheduler from Calendar
    Then click on Save
